New Features & Benefits
Smart Greetings:

Feature: Greets you with "Good morning," "Good afternoon," or "Good evening" based on the current time.
Benefit: Makes the app feel more personal and aware of the time of day.
Friendly Emojis:

Feature: Adds a fun emoji (like 😊, ☀️, or 🌙) that matches the time of day.
Benefit: Makes the greeting more visually appealing and adds a touch of personality.
VIP Treatment for Sumaya:

Feature: Displays a unique, special message if you enter "Sumaya."
Benefit: Allows the app to recognize and give a special shout-out to specific important users.
Special Greeting Feature & Benefit
Custom VIP Welcome:
Feature: If the user ens "Sumaya" (regardless of capitalization), they get a unique and more elaborate welcome message.
Benefit: This creates a highly personalized experience, making a specific user feel recognized and valued, adding a special touch beyond a standard greeting.
Standard Greeting Template:

Feature: Provides a consistent, framed welcome message ("Welcome to the Hello World App!" and "We're glad to have you here!") for all users, with a placeholder for the user's name.
Benefit: Ensures every user receives a clear, friendly, and branded greeting, maintaining consistency across non-special interactions.
